{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, in the sentence 'The food was delicious, and the staff was wonderful', the primary topics returned by Keyphrase Extraction would be 'food' and 'wonderful staff '.",
    "The Keyphrase Extraction process is performed in two stages: candidate generation, where all possible keywords are identified from the input text, and keyphrase ranking, where the candidate keywords are ranked in order of importance.",
    "We applied this method to the entire document collection in the dataset and identified the documents that discussed a CT.",
    "This resulted in a labeled dataset that we used subsequently to train our classifier.",
    "We adopted the keyphrase-extraction-kbir-inspec tool from the Hugging Face platform [54], a repository of NLP models and datasets."
  ]
}